Crystals were harvested and soaked overnight in a solution containing 100 mM PCPT, 35% PEG 3350, 200 mM Mg2Cl and 1-2 mM TK-666 from a 100 mM DMSO stock. After soaking the crystals were cryoprotected by soaking for 15 minutes in compound-soak solution supplemented with 20% ethylene glycol. , VAPOR DIFFUSION, SITTING DROP
